more of the servo twitch out of Spazbot, I found time to update the
web site!  http://nfn.no-ip.com     I registered with the Dynamic DNS
nameserver, lets see how well it works.  Just before my DHCP lease
expire
I kill -HUP pump (dhcp client) and force update my ip addess.  I then
run my DHCP client code and update my dns entry. Right now they update
ever 4 hours so I do this on a Sunay morning at 4:00 AM, 25th of every
month.  I am now looking for MPEG encoders for Linux that way the
